{"title":"Featured Products","description":"","products":[{"product_id":"honeysticks-originals-12pk","title":"Honeysticks Beeswax Crayons Originals 12pk","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"OutlineElement Ltr SCXW23206258 BCX8\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eOur \u003cstrong\u003eHoneysticks Beeswax Crayons Originals 12pk\u003c\/strong\u003e are a best-seller for a reason - they're the perfect first crayon. Ideal for toddlers aged 1-3, Originals have a short, stubby design made especially for little hands - easy to grip yet tough to break. Handcrafted from pure New Zealand beeswax, they're a safe, sustainable way to introduce your little artist to a world of pure creation.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eThe perfect first crayon:\u003c\/strong\u003e The unique chubby shape of Honeysticks Originals makes them easier for small hands to hold, but much harder for small hands to break! Each crayon is 55mm long and 20mm in diameter.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eNatural + food-grade ingredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Handmade using 100% pure New Zealand beeswax and food-grade pigments for colour. Non-toxic and safe for toddlers and children, with no paraffin wax or cheap fillers.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eSustainable and low impact:\u003c\/strong\u003e The beeswax used to create Honeysticks is a natural by-product of honey production. This sustainable process causes minimal impact on the environment and gives the crayons a wonderful honey scent.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003e12 exciting colours:\u003c\/strong\u003e Get creative and explore! Our food-grade colours easily bond to the paper, posters or artboard.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eHandcrafted by families, for families: \u003c\/strong\u003eDesigned by parents who believe in a better way to play, Honeysticks Originals are handmade in New Zealand to inspire creativity from the very first scribble.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cem\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eNow, in our refreshed Honeysticks look - welcome to a world of pure creation!\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/em\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"Honeysticks UK","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":56350549213565,"sku":"HCROR12","price":17.95,"currency_code":"GBP","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0553\/5465\/4896\/files\/Originals12pk.png?v=1765163773"},{"product_id":"honeysticks-bath-crayon-super-jumbos","title":"Honeysticks Bath Crayons Super Jumbos 7pk","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"OutlineElement Ltr SCXW160703923 BCX8\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"OutlineElement Ltr SCXW203348273 BCX8\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan lang=\"EN-NZ\" data-contrast=\"auto\"\u003e\u003cspan data-ccp-parastyle-defn='{\"ObjectId\":\"5608de39-acc8-52c5-8723-06e2503f1031|1\",\"ClassId\":1073872969,\"Properties\":[469777841,\"Times New Roman\",469777842,\"Times New Roman\",469777843,\"Times New Roman\",469777844,\"Times New Roman\",469769226,\"Times New Roman\",268442635,\"24\",335559705,\"2057\",335551547,\"5129\",335559740,\"240\",201341983,\"0\",335559739,\"0\",201342446,\"1\",201342447,\"5\",201342448,\"3\",201342449,\"1\",201341986,\"1\",469775450,\"p1\",201340122,\"2\",134233614,\"true\",469778129,\"p1\",335572020,\"1\",134233118,\"true\",134233117,\"true\",469778324,\"Normal\"]}' data-ccp-parastyle=\"p1\"\u003eAdd a splash of creativity to your little one’s bath time with \u003cstrong\u003eHoneysticks Bath Crayons Super Jumbos 7pk\u003c\/strong\u003e. Made with 100% pure New Zealand beeswax and soy wax, these chunky crayons are safe on skin, gentle on the planet, and a joy for curious young creators.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan data-ccp-parastyle=\"p1\"\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan data-ccp-props='{\"134233117\":true,\"134233118\":true,\"201341983\":0,\"335559739\":0,\"335559740\":240}'\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003e\u003cspan lang=\"EN-NZ\" data-contrast=\"auto\"\u003e\u003cspan data-ccp-charstyle-defn='{\"ObjectId\":\"65adc4b8-9fe6-5d96-a288-b4732a2d40b3|1\",\"ClassId\":1073872969,\"Properties\":[201342446,\"1\",201342447,\"5\",201342448,\"3\",201342449,\"1\",469777841,\"Cambria\",469777842,\"\",469777843,\"ＭＳ 明朝\",469777844,\"Cambria\",201341986,\"1\",469769226,\"Cambria,ＭＳ 明朝\",268442635,\"22\",469775450,\"s1\",201340122,\"1\",134233614,\"true\",469778129,\"s1\",335572020,\"1\",469778324,\"Default Paragraph Font\"]}' data-ccp-charstyle=\"s1\"\u003eMade with nothing nasty:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003cspan lang=\"EN-NZ\" data-contrast=\"auto\"\u003e\u003cspan data-ccp-parastyle=\"p1\"\u003e Crafted in New Zealand using natural and food-grade ingredients – no paraffin wax, no artificial fillers.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan data-ccp-props='{\"134233117\":true,\"134233118\":true,\"201341983\":0,\"335559739\":0,\"335559740\":240}'\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003e\u003cspan data-ccp-charstyle=\"s1\"\u003eSpark their imagination:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\" lang=\"EN-NZ\" data-contrast=\"auto\"\u003e\u003cspan data-ccp-parastyle=\"p1\"\u003e With s\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan data-ccp-parastyle=\"p1\"\u003eeven \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan data-ccp-parastyle=\"p1\"\u003evibrant colours to explore, kids can doodle, mix, and colour their way through bath time.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\" data-ccp-props='{\"134233117\":true,\"134233118\":true,\"201341983\":0,\"335559739\":0,\"335559740\":240}'\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003e\u003cspan data-ccp-charstyle=\"s1\"\u003eChunky, \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan data-ccp-charstyle=\"s1\"\u003edurable\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan data-ccp-charstyle=\"s1\"\u003e and easy to hold\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan data-ccp-charstyle=\"s1\"\u003e:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\" lang=\"EN-NZ\" data-contrast=\"auto\"\u003e\u003cspan data-ccp-parastyle=\"p1\"\u003e Extra-long and easy to hold (10cm x 2cm), these crayons are designed for toddlers aged 1+.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\" data-ccp-props='{\"134233117\":true,\"134233118\":true,\"201341983\":0,\"335559739\":0,\"335559740\":240}'\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003e\u003cspan data-ccp-charstyle=\"s1\"\u003eWipe off, walk away:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\" lang=\"EN-NZ\" data-contrast=\"auto\"\u003e\u003cspan data-ccp-parastyle=\"p1\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e \u003c\/strong\u003eColours rinse away easily with warm water and a soft cloth – no scrubbing needed.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\" data-ccp-props='{\"134233117\":true,\"134233118\":true,\"201341983\":0,\"335559739\":0,\"335559740\":240}'\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003e\u003cspan data-ccp-charstyle=\"s1\"\u003eDesigned for bathroom play:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\" lang=\"EN-NZ\" data-contrast=\"auto\"\u003e\u003cspan data-ccp-parastyle=\"p1\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e \u003c\/strong\u003ePackaged in a resealable, drainable canister that’s plastic-free and doubles as a fun bath-time sprinkler toy.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\" data-ccp-props='{\"134233117\":true,\"134233118\":true,\"201341983\":0,\"335559739\":0,\"335559740\":240}'\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003e\u003cspan data-ccp-charstyle=\"s1\"\u003eHandcrafted by families, for families:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\" lang=\"EN-NZ\" data-contrast=\"auto\"\u003e\u003cspan data-ccp-parastyle=\"p1\"\u003e Designed by parents who believe in a better way to play, Honeysticks Super Jumbo Bath Crayons are lovingly handmade in New Zealand to encourage creative expression from the very first scribble.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\" data-ccp-props='{\"134233117\":true,\"134233118\":true,\"201341983\":0,\"335559739\":0,\"335559740\":240}'\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003e\u003cspan data-ccp-parastyle=\"p1\"\u003eAlso available:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\" lang=\"EN-NZ\" data-contrast=\"auto\"\u003e\u003cspan data-ccp-parastyle=\"p1\"\u003e Our easy-grip Triangle Bath Crayons – perfect for first-time scribblers.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\" data-ccp-props='{\"134233117\":true,\"134233118\":true,\"201341983\":0,\"335559739\":0,\"335559740\":240}'\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cem\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e\u003cspan lang=\"EN-NZ\" data-contrast=\"auto\"\u003e\u003cspan data-ccp-parastyle-defn='{\"ObjectId\":\"b71b86aa-d72c-5c05-bc38-eb0d9113b743|1\",\"ClassId\":1073872969,\"Properties\":[469777841,\"Times New Roman\",469777842,\"Times New Roman\",469777843,\"Times New Roman\",469777844,\"Times New Roman\",469769226,\"Times New Roman\",268442635,\"24\",335559705,\"2057\",335551547,\"5129\",335559740,\"240\",201341983,\"0\",335559739,\"0\",201342446,\"1\",201342447,\"5\",201342448,\"3\",201342449,\"1\",201341986,\"1\",469775450,\"p4\",201340122,\"2\",134233614,\"true\",469778129,\"p4\",335572020,\"1\",134233118,\"true\",134233117,\"true\",469778324,\"Normal\"]}' data-ccp-parastyle=\"p4\"\u003eNow, in our refreshed Honeysticks look – welcome to a world of pure creation!\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan data-ccp-props='{\"134233117\":true,\"134233118\":true,\"201341983\":0,\"335559739\":0,\"335559740\":240}'\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/em\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"Honeysticks UK","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":56350550163837,"sku":"HBTSJ7","price":17.95,"currency_code":"GBP","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0553\/5465\/4896\/files\/BathCrayonsSJs.webp?v=1765227859"},{"product_id":"honeysticks-bubble-bath","title":"Honeysticks Bubble Bath Colour Mixing 3pk 220ml","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"SCXW85038921 BCX8\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"OutlineElement Ltr SCXW85038921 BCX8\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"SCXW267638514 BCX8\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"OutlineElement Ltr SCXW267638514 BCX8\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-contrast=\"auto\" lang=\"EN-NZ\"\u003e\u003cspan data-ccp-parastyle=\"p4\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eBring colour mixing to the tub!\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-contrast=\"auto\" lang=\"EN-NZ\"\u003e\u003cspan data-ccp-parastyle=\"p4\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHoneysticks Bubble Bath Colour Mixing 3pk 220ml\u003c\/strong\u003e transforms bath time into a playful, hands-on experiment in colour and creativity. With three mixable colours and a plant-based formula, kids can create six vibrant shades – all while enjoying soft, super-foamy bubbles. Fun bee-shaped bottles add to the magic.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan data-ccp-props='{\"134233117\":true,\"134233118\":true,\"201341983\":0,\"335559739\":0,\"335559740\":240}'\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003e\u003cspan data-contrast=\"auto\" lang=\"EN-NZ\"\u003e\u003cspan data-ccp-charstyle=\"s1\" data-ccp-charstyle-defn='{\"ObjectId\":\"65adc4b8-9fe6-5d96-a288-b4732a2d40b3|1\",\"ClassId\":1073872969,\"Properties\":[201342446,\"1\",201342447,\"5\",201342448,\"3\",201342449,\"1\",469777841,\"Cambria\",469777842,\"\",469777843,\"ＭＳ 明朝\",469777844,\"Cambria\",201341986,\"1\",469769226,\"Cambria,ＭＳ 明朝\",268442635,\"22\",469775450,\"s1\",201340122,\"1\",134233614,\"true\",469778129,\"s1\",335572020,\"1\",469778324,\"Default Paragraph Font\"]}'\u003eThree colours, six shades to explore:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003cspan data-contrast=\"auto\" lang=\"EN-NZ\"\u003e\u003cspan data-ccp-charstyle=\"s1\"\u003e Includes red, yellow, and blue bottles – little creators can use them solo or mix to make a rainbow of six \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan data-ccp-charstyle=\"s1\"\u003epossible shades\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan data-ccp-charstyle=\"s1\"\u003e.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan data-ccp-props='{\"134233117\":true,\"134233118\":true,\"201341983\":0,\"335559739\":0,\"335559740\":240}'\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003e\u003cspan data-ccp-charstyle=\"s1\"\u003eSuper-foaming, naturally: \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003cspan data-contrast=\"auto\" lang=\"EN-NZ\" style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"\u003e\u003cspan data-ccp-charstyle=\"s1\"\u003eSwirl under warm running water to whip up soft, fluffy bubbles and bring bath-time to life! Made with plant-based ingredients and cosmetic-grade pigments – no parabens, phthalates, or synthetic fragrances.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan data-ccp-props='{\"134233117\":true,\"134233118\":true,\"201341983\":0,\"335559739\":0,\"335559740\":240}' style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003e\u003cspan data-ccp-charstyle=\"s1\"\u003eFun bee-shaped bottles, planet-friendly packaging: \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003cspan data-contrast=\"auto\" lang=\"EN-NZ\" style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"\u003e\u003cspan data-ccp-charstyle=\"s1\"\u003eEach 220ml bottle is made from 100% reclaimed plastic and packed in recyclable, PEFC-certified cardboard. Designed for little hands and big imaginations.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan data-ccp-props='{\"134233117\":true,\"134233118\":true,\"201341983\":0,\"335559739\":0,\"335559740\":240}' style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003e\u003cspan data-ccp-charstyle=\"s1\"\u003eSafe for children 1+: \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003cspan data-contrast=\"auto\" lang=\"EN-NZ\" style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"\u003e\u003cspan data-ccp-charstyle=\"s1\"\u003eOur gentle, plant-based formula is rigorously safety tested for little creators aged 12 months and up. Made without SLS, parabens, phthalates, or synthetic fragrances. Colour comes from cosmetic and food-grade pigments.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan data-ccp-props='{\"134233117\":true,\"134233118\":true,\"201341983\":0,\"335559739\":0,\"335559740\":240}' style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan data-ccp-charstyle=\"s1\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eSo easy to clean up:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan data-contrast=\"auto\" lang=\"EN-NZ\" style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"\u003e\u003cspan data-ccp-charstyle=\"s1\"\u003eSimply rinse the colourful water and bubbles down the drain – no stains on skin or bathroom surfaces.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan data-ccp-props='{\"134233117\":true,\"134233118\":true,\"201341983\":0,\"335559739\":0,\"335559740\":240}' style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003e\u003cspan data-ccp-charstyle=\"s1\"\u003eDesigned by parents who believe in a better way to play:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003cspan data-contrast=\"auto\" lang=\"EN-NZ\" style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"\u003e\u003cspan data-ccp-parastyle=\"p1